teuer nicht bezahlt haben</rs></term></keywords></textClass></profileDesc><revisionDesc><change n=""><date>2008-12-23</date><respStmt><name>IDP</name></respStmt><item>Automated split from transcoder files</item></change><change n="meta.18867"><date>02.02.1995</date><respStmt><name>HGV</name></respStmt><item>Record created</item></change><change n="meta.18867"><date>13.11.2007</date><respStmt><name>HGV</name></respStmt><item>Record last modified</item></change><change n="meta.18867"><date>2009-03-20</date><respStmt><name>IDP</name></respStmt><item>Crosswalked to EpiDoc XML</item></change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><head lang="en"><date>AD697/712</date>
<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Thebes</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>ἐν ὀνόματι το[ῦ <expan>θ<ex cert="high">εο</ex></expan>ῦ <expan>φιλανθ]ρώ<ex cert="high">που</ex></expan>, 

    <lb n="2"/>ἐλεήμονος. <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="3"/><gap reason="ellipsis" desc="Arabic" extent="1" unit="line"/> 

    <lb n="4"/>οὐκ ἔστιν <expan>θ<ex cert="high">εὸ</ex></expan>ς εἰ μὴ ὁ <expan>θ<ex cert="high">εὸ</ex></expan>ς μόνος. 

    <lb n="5"/>Μααμετ ἀπόστολος θεοῦ. 

    <lb n="6"/><gap reason="ellipsis" desc="Arabic" extent="1" unit="line"/> 

    <lb n="7"/>Ἀβδελαζιζ υἱὸς 

    <lb n="8"/>Μαρουαν σύμβουλος. <expan>ἰ<ex cert="high">νδικτίωνος</ex></expan> <num value="8"><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">η</unclear></num>. 

    <lb n="9"/><g type="stauros"/> σὺν <expan>θ<ex cert="high">εῷ</ex></expan>. <expan>Φλά<ex cert="high">ουιος</ex></expan> Ἀτίας <expan>υἱὸ<ex cert="high">ς</ex></expan> Γοεδου ὑμῖν τοῖς κατοικοῦσι Καύκοις εἰς τὸ ὄρος Μεμνονίων. 

    <lb n="10"/>ἐπείπερ ψηλαφήσαντός μου τὸν λόγον τῶν ἐπιζητουμένων δι᾽ ὑμῶν 

    <lb n="11"/>ἀπὸ διαγράφου καὶ θελήσαντός μου ἀπαιτῆσαι ὑμᾶς τὸ τοιοῦτο διάγραφον, 

    <lb n="12"/>ὥσπερ καὶ τὰ λοιπὰ μοναστήρια <choice><corr>δίδοντα</corr><sic>διδουντα</sic></choice> τὰ διάγραφα αὐτῶν διὰ τὸ 

    <lb n="13"/>ἀγνωμονῆσαι <hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi>μᾶς ἐν καιρῷ τῆς ἀνταρσίας, προεκομίσατέ μοι σιγίλλιν 

    <lb n="14"/>Οὐοειθ τοῦ ποτε διοικήσαντος τὴν ἄνω χώραν περιέχον τοῦ μεῖναι ὑμᾶς 

    <lb n="15"/>εἰς τὸν τόπον ὑμῶν συντελοῦντας μέντοι τὰ διάγραφα ὑμῶν, καὶ ἐπιβεβαίων 

    <lb n="16"/>τὸ <choice><corr>τοι<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">ο</supplied>ῦτο</corr><sic>τοιυτο</sic></choice> σιγίλλιν τῷ παρόντι σιγιλλίῳ ἐχρησάμην, δι᾽ οὗ <choice><corr>ἐπιτρέπω</corr><sic>επιτρεπωω</sic></choice> ὑμῖν 

    <lb n="17"/>ἀφόβως μεῖναι τῇ ταυτότητι εἰς τὸν τόπον ὑμῶν καὶ λόγον ἔχειν τοῦ μὴ 

    <lb n="18"/>συγχωρῆσαί με παρελθεῖν δι᾽ ὑμῶν τινα,<g type="apostrophe"/> ὑμῶν μέντοι φυλαττόντων 

    <lb n="19"/>τὴν εἰρηναίαν ὑμῶν κατάστασιν καὶ συντελούντων τὸ διάγραφον ὑμῶν, 

    <lb n="20"/>ὅπερ ἠγνωμονήσατε ὡς εἴρηται ἐν καιρῷ τῆς ἀνταρσίας·<g type="apostrophe"/> καὶ πρὸς τὸ 

    <lb n="21"/>δῆλον εἶναι τῷ παρόντι σιγιλλίῳ ἐχρησάμην, ἐπιτεθεικὼς αὐτῷ καὶ 

    <lb n="22"/>τὴν ἐμὴν βοῦλλαν. ἐγράφη <expan>μη<ex cert="high">νὶ</ex></expan> <expan>Φαῶφ<ex cert="high">ι</ex></expan> <num value="20">κ</num>, <expan>ἰνδ<ex cert="high">ικτίων</ex>ο<ex cert="high">ς</ex></expan> ἑνδεκάτης. <g type="stauros"/> 

    <lb n="23"/><figure><figDesc>seal</figDesc></figure> </ab></div><div n="meta.18867" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.18867" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" value="0697-10-17" notBefore="697" notAfter="697">17. Okt. 697</date></p></div><div n="meta.18867" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Zur Datierung vgl. BL VIII, S. 326 - 327. Griechisch - arabisch. Gehört zum Archiv des Flavius Atias (vgl. CPR VIII, S. 192).</p></div><div n="meta.18867" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head><p>Z. 8: <date type="mentioned" notBefore="0694" notAfter="0695">694 - 695</date></p></div><div n="meta.18867" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">SB</title><biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">7240</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">18867</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0239</series>; <biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">7240</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0239;3;7240" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.18867" type="bibliography" subtype="corrections" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">326/327</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">XI</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">201</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></di